---
title: Tex-Mex Turkey and Rice Skillet with Cheddar and Lime Crema
description: This colourful, no-fuss Tex-Mex skillet is packed with flavour from perfectly spiced rice and salsa-coated turkey and peppers, then topped with melty cheese and cilantro. A dollop of lime crema is all you need to make your tastebuds sing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poelee-de-riz-a-la-dinde-tex-mex-e5fcc63a.jpg
